			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				How to get &quot;Nathyn's Memoirs&quot; without a rogue or key.<BR>
Get a druid to change to wolf form (preferably in the opposite empty room that's unlocked).<BR>
Invis up, go to locked door, sit down right up against the door with your wolf face poking through the door. Mem Egress or gate spell.<BR>
Camp out &amp; log back in.<BR>
&quot;Presto&quot;, you will log in, inside the room. Grab the book on the table &amp; gate or Egress out.<BR>
Believe me, THIS WORKS! I know, I did it myself &amp; I have the book.<BR>
BTW, no coterie spawned when I grabbed the book. Maybe the door opening &amp; closing triggers him.<BR>
<BR>
Question: Does anyone know the exact loc of Peqi? Since he's on such a long timer, I have no idea where to find him &amp; couldn't pick him up on track.
